{"tid":1988149,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情下美國人領養寵物激增 收容中心慶祝犬舍清空","createTime":"2020-04-25T04:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T13:13:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4069c285548f49f607c00160413f3a615b3e2040","tid":1988149,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情下，美國民眾的社交活動要暫停，此時寵物成為人類克服寂寞的最佳夥伴。最近美國各地流浪動物的領養需求急增，佛羅里達州一處收容所更首見有犬舍清空，該收容所的義工拍手慶祝，成為疫情期間難得的好消息。<br />\n<br />\n佛州棕櫚灘（Palm Beach）一間動物收容所上周在Facebook上載影片，可見戴口罩的義工拍手慶祝第一次有犬舍清空。報道指，這是該間收容所有史以來第一次、3棟犬舍中其中之一被清空。收容所代表指出，在社區的努力下，流浪動物陸續找到寄養家庭或新主人，遺棄的案例正在減少。<br />\n<br />\n居家令擴及全國，民眾待在家中除了有更多時間下廚、專注園藝、陪伴家人以外，更有餘力飼養寵物，從東岸到西岸，各地的動物收容所申請領養的數字大增。美國愛護動物協會（ASPCA）會長伯沙德克爾（Matt Bershadker）表示，紐約與洛杉磯兩大城市的寄養數字比去年同期增加了70%。洛杉磯愛護動物協會統計，今年3月有307隻動物找到寄養家庭、919隻動物找到新主人。<br />\n<br />\n領養寵物的過程亦要遵守防疫規定，保持社交距離。民眾可上網登記，成為暫時的寄養家庭或永久領養。收容機構透過電話與申請人面談，申請通過之後，寄養或領養者可開車到收容所的停車場等候，然後在路邊領走貓狗。<br />\n<br />\n不過有收容機構擔心，隨着美國失業人口恐達2,000萬，有些家庭可能無法負擔飼養寵物的費用。為了避免斷糧的情況，大部份收容機構提供飼料給有需要的寄養家庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200424/large/1587737051_c033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200424%2Flarge%2F1587737051_c033.jpg&h=1a87f062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200425/J56A4DSZL3PES7IZ5STDPUWGJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200425%2FJ56A4DSZL3PES7IZ5STDPUWGJ4%2F&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKjrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=3dfc0eb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200425%2FJ56A4DSZL3PES7IZ5STDPUWGJ4%2F&h=b7057711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200425/J56A4DSZL3PES7IZ5STDPUWGJ4/</a>"},{"pid":"596bd86ebad29468fad4d12eae58cd6c6ba00157","tid":1988149,"uid":10637,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"疫情過後d寵物又返返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4546e18b7053dcf222a6a63f475f3d591352335","tid":1988149,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"咁又可以炒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea850bf5e6e3b0dbb790ce41d45afb86fbfac70","tid":1988149,"uid":145873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"一完疫情就掉返哂出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec9d4dfefe278207371746c9270ecdf1548cce1","tid":1988149,"uid":201751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ccce2618ffcec752fee6d7e72fa06fb2a82fdc","tid":1988149,"uid":136226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"慶祝失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7abca7c8fd96c71e842741bb9e5b846cc7a15e","tid":1988149,"uid":299372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:13:02.000Z","msg":"疫情下中國人殺晒自己屋企d寵物<br />\n好多單扔屋企隻狗/貓落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}